name: Moors of Ykesha
notes: This huge ancient swamp is the chief base of operations for the Gunthak Pirates, and the ancestral homeland for the frogloks of Norrath. Places of legend, such as the ruins of Guk and the city of Grobb can be found here, as well as anchors to the alternate dimension known as the Void.

npcs.name: a Chronomage
utterances: Step on in to the Chronoweave, adventurer. Do not be nervous. We have stabilized the chronoportals, I assure you.

We've come to a strong enough understanding of the ebb and flow of the chrono stream, after years of study, to recognize this as the annual phase in which the barrier to the stream of the past is the thinnest.

npcs.name: Gabblin Bittlegrip
utterances: Look at all the magnificent things we've already found in this short time!  There must be so much more out in the Moors just waiting to be discovered!

npcs.name: a mysterious Quellithulian
utterances: You needn't ask how I acquired these items. Be thankful I offer them up to you at such reasonable prices.
Remarkable items can be manufactured from these void shards.  I will be happy to take any off your hands.

npcs.name: Skymaster Akiz Hoopster
utterances: The Skystrider will be arriving from the The Sinking Sands shortly.
The Skystrider will be leaving for the The Sinking Sands in 62 seconds.
The Skystrider has left for the The Sinking Sands, it will be returning soon.
The Skystrider is currently in the The Sinking Sands.
